        <abstract> 
<p>Sends CD cheque for £250, two-thirds of the profits on the sale of 700 copies of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>, 4th ed.</p>  
<p>Hopes he has found a suitable indexer for <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>.</p> 
